Minimal example showing the insertion point in the stock 3.3.5a GlueParent.xml layout:

<Ui xmlns="http://www.blizzard.com/wow/ui/"
    xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
    xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.blizzard.com/wow/ui/ ..\FrameXML\UI.xsd">
    <Script file="GlueParent.lua"/>
    <Include file="GlueXML\DarkChaos\DarkChaosBreakingNews.xml"/>

    <Frame name="GlueParent" setAllPoints="true">
        ...
    </Frame>
</Ui>

Notes:
- The important part is that DarkChaosBreakingNews.xml is loaded from GlueParent.xml.
- GlueParent.lua stays unchanged.